publisher			Plug In Digital, Milestone S.r.l.							
publish_time	 2013年6月20日		
desc_long									最新更新									Additional riders, bikes and teams are now available to expand your gaming experience by completing the in-game rosters of the Moto2™ and Moto3™ categories. This free of charge additional content is totally updated for the 2013 season, for a comprehensive immersion in MotoGP™ world.																						关于这款游戏							2013 Riders, teams and tracks; both simulation and accessible bike handling with scalable aids; photorealistic graphics with TV style interface; ingame voice over by official MotoGP™ commentators;  first person elements such as the helmet view and 3D pits to put you in the rider’s shoes. This is MotoGP™13, the official MotoGP™ videogame: try Career Mode, rising from a Moto3™ wildcard to the MotoGP™ World Champion, or challenge your friends in Split Screen or Online Championship.						
